article.description: — Logan Bracamonte had 15 points and seven rebounds, Keaston Willis also scored 15 points and Incarnate Word defeated Texas A&M-Corpus Christi 72-53 on Saturday.
article.headline: Incarnate Word defeats Texas A&M-Corpus Christi 72-53
article.linkText: Incarnate Word defeats Texas A&M-Corpus Christi 72-53
article.story: SAN ANTONIO -- — Logan Bracamonte had 15 points and seven rebounds, Keaston Willis also scored 15 points and Incarnate Word defeated Texas A&M-Corpus Christi 72-53 on Saturday. Des Balentine added seven rebounds and six assists for the Cardinals (6-6, 3-2 Southland Conference). Jalen White had 17 points for the Islanders (3-9, 0-3). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
